ROADMAP

Quick outline:   NOTE This is a general and rough guidline, this project is in it's VERY
                 early stages.

Proposed Modular structure:

Install Module     Handles installation database settings, auth type etc..
Auth Module        Handle Authentication: LDAP/DBAUTH etc.
Marketing Module   Handles marketing services.
Services Module	   Handles customer services.
Sales Module       Handles Sales services.
Contacts Module    Handles contact management.
